---
// src/pages/privacy-policy.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = "June 2025"; // EDIT: Update this date when you revise this page
---

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    background: var(--grad-hero);
    padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .legal-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-meta { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-body {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }
  .legal-body h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .legal-body h2:first-of-type { border-top: none; margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-body p  { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.97rem; }
  .legal-body ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .legal-body ul li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .legal-body a  { color: var(--coral); }
</style>

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Smart Reward Finds"
  description="Smart Reward Finds Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="legal-body container">

    <p>
      Welcome to Smart Reward Finds (<strong>smartrewardfinds.com</strong>). Your privacy is important to us.
      This Privacy Policy explains what information we may collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.
      By using this website, you agree to the practices described in this policy.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Information you provide directly:</strong> When you submit our contact form, we collect your name,
        email address, phone number (if provided), reason for contact, and message content.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Automatically collected information:</strong> Like most websites, we may collect certain
        information automatically when you visit, such as your IP address, browser type, operating system,
        referring URLs, and pages visited. This may be done through analytics tools (see Section 3).
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Cookies:</strong> We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve your experience.
        You can control cookies through your browser settings.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to your inquiries submitted through our contact form</li>
      <li>Improve the content and functionality of this website</li>
      <li>Understand how visitors use our site (through analytics)</li>
      <li>Send you updates or newsletters, if you have opted in (we do not currently send newsletters without consent)</li>
      <li>Maintain the security and operation of this site</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We may use third-party analytics services such as Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with
      our site. These services may collect information about your visit using cookies and similar technologies.
      This data is aggregated and anonymized where possible. You can opt out of Google Analytics by using the
      <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Affiliate Links &amp; Third Parties</h2>
    <p>
      Smart Reward Finds contains links to third-party websites and services, including affiliate and partner links.
      When you click these links and visit third-party sites, those sites have their own privacy policies that govern
      the collection and use of your data. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of third-party sites.
    </p>
    <p>
      For more information about how we handle affiliate relationships, please see our
      <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Contact Form Submissions</h2>
    <p>
      When you submit our contact form, your data is transmitted to a third-party form processing service
      (such as Formspree or Google Forms) and may be stored in a connected service (such as Google Sheets)
      for the purpose of responding to your inquiry. We do not sell or share this data with other parties
      for marketing purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Newsletter / Email Communications</h2>
    <p>
      If we offer a newsletter or email subscription in the future, we will use a reputable email service provider
      and you will always have the option to unsubscribe. We will not add you to any mailing list without
      your explicit consent.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      We retain contact form submissions as long as necessary to respond to your inquiry and for reasonable
      record-keeping. If you would like your data removed, please contact us using the information below.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      This website is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
      information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please
      contact us and we will take steps to remove it.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal data, including the right
      to access, correct, or request deletion of your data. To exercise these rights, please contact us at the
      address below.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will update the "Last updated" date
      at the top of this page. Continued use of this site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
    </p>

    <h2>11. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please use our
      <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to get in touch.
    </p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
